platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Everyones suspicious in Among Us!, a fascinating multiplayer game set aboard a damaged spaceship. Whether youre a Crewmate making quick repairs or an Impostor taking out key systems (and unsuspecting players), each match is a riveting mystery. And a hilarious one, especially when smart accusations or sly misdirection sway who gets voted off the ship. Its a test of wits anyone can enjoy.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: Customize your look with Halloween-themed hats.
